      "side": 1,
      "message": "So where exactly should I be setting this field?\n\nCrashReportDatabaseGeneric::CheckoutReport() seems to be the underlying method most other methods uses to construct a Report, but it is CrashReportDatabaseGeneric specific. For Windows, it seems that the Records come from records_ augmented in Metadata::AddNewRecord(). For Mac, there is at least CrashReportDatabaseMac::ReportsInDirectory() that creates Reports.\n\nI am fine to make it a field in Report as this was my first idea. I just found it hard to track down all the places where we construct a Report.",
