      "message": "The only thing that creates Report objects is the Database. But there are different implementations depending on platform, so there are a few locations to add it. I\u0027d probably put it in:\n\n- CrashReportDatabaseGeneric::ReadMetadata\n- CrashReportDatabaseMac::ReadReportMetadataLocked\n- Metadata::FindSingleReport and ::FindReports in _win (Scott can speak up if he thinks there\u0027s a better place).\n\nOn Windows we don\u0027t want to keep the size in the metadata sidecar file; we want to compute it when producing a ReportDisk.",
